snippet.title: Rekka Rekka | Bison Kaalamaadan | Dhruv Vikram, Anupama | Mari Selvaraj | Nivas K Prasanna | Arivu
snippet.description:
Rekka Rekka is a high-energy Tamil track that blends folk and electronic elements from the movie Bison Kaalamaadan, with music by Nivas K. Prasanna.  The song is a collaboration between singer-lyricist Arivu and singer Vedan, with Mari Selvaraj & Arivu penning the powerful lyrics.

snippet.title: Two Much With Kajol And Twinkle - Official Trailer | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Two Much With Kajol And Twinkle Official Trailer
Starring Kajol, Twinkle Khanna, Salman Khan, Aamir Khan, Govinda, Chunky Panday, Vicky Kaushal, Kriti Sanon, Varun Dhawan, Alia Bhatt, Janhvi Kapoor, Karan Johar.
Created by Banijay Asia

Official Release Date September 25, 2025 on Prime Video India.

About:
Kajol and Twinkle are serving up a talk show with a twist - equal parts masti, magic and maybe even some manic energy. Expect wild hot takes, controversial opinions and the kind of honesty that makes you say, ‚ÄúDude, same!‚Äù 
Joining them are their friends who just happen to be some of the biggest stars in the country (and even the world). With eight unique pairs gracing the couch this season, the conversations jump from filmy nostalgia to family drama, love, paparazzi, fame and everything in between.
What sets it apart is the unapologetic female gaze - a perspective that‚Äôs funny, sharp, and not afraid to hold up a mirror to society. One moment you‚Äôre laughing embarrassingly loudly, the next you‚Äôre caught off guard by an insight that might make you question your own life choices. 
Basically, it‚Äôs a vibe: two women side-by-side, yapping with their friends. Think of it as the fun table at the party, sunny, chatty, and just unhinged enough to keep you hooked.

Additionally, Prime Video‚Äôs video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures ‚Äì Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Jio Saavn - https://www.jiosaavn.com/song/not-like-you/GT4yZTUFU2M
Gaana - https://gaana.com/song/not-like-you-147

#Peesa #Nolikeyou #Latestharyanvisong #Hammymuzic #Trendingssong #Thailandkavisathodihu #Joharkiseneachelaagu #peesathodihu 

#haryanvihiphop #desihiphop #haryanvirap #hiphopindia  #haryanvisong  #haryanvimusic #haryanvisong2025 #newharyanvisong #newharyanvisong2025 #indianhiphop 

Lyrics 

Mera dekh ke time re  badiya 
Hoyi khraab re inki ghadiya 
Re mein thook ke konya chaatu 
Saale kutto thari tariyaan 

Milje  jane khane ne 
thailand ka visa thodi hu 

Jo Har kise ne acha laagu re mein pissa thodi hu 
Matlab khatar laau yaari thare jissa thodi hu 

Mehngi Dekh ke Bottle Daaru ki ye Rang Badal le 
System dekh ke tagda bolan ka ye dhang badal le 
Jitni bhookh se bhadri inke bhitar pise ki 
Thode time mein laage private na ye ang badal le 

 lelu jane Khane ne god mein mother terresa thodi hu 

Re ye Kutte Bille soche meri gaillan dodan ki 
Har ek badnaami ne soche ye meri gailan jodan ki 
Ye  zero te hero bhi mane  bna rakhe 
Bawlipuch ye fer bhi chave meri legacy todan ki 

Maar ke pathar tod je hammy ne mein shisha thodi hu

Jo Har kise ne acha laagu re mein pissa thodi hu 
Matlab khatar laau yaari thare jissa thodi hu

We respect every individual regardless of ability and stand firmly against discrimination or mockery of any kind.

THE HOUSEMAID is a wildly entertaining thriller starring Sydney Sweeney and Amanda Seyfried, based on the best-selling book. From director Paul Feig, the film plunges audiences into a twisted world where perfection is an illusion, and nothing is as it seems. Trying to escape her past, Millie (Sweeney) accepts a job as a live-in housemaid for the wealthy Nina (Seyfried) and Andrew Winchester (Brandon Sklenar). But what begins as a dream job quickly unravels into something far more dangerous ‚Äì a sexy, seductive game of secrets, scandal, and power. Behind the Winchesters‚Äô closed doors lies a world of shocking twists that will leave you guessing until the very end.

snippet.title: His Grace (Official Music Video) - Ndee Kundu & Bintu Pabra | New Haryanvi Song 2025 | Real Music
snippet.description:
Presenting the new Haryanvi song 2025 ‚Äì His Grace | Ndee Kundu & Bintu Pabra 

"His Grace" by Ndee Kundu & Bintu Pabra is a soulful Haryanvi track that blends emotions, powerful storytelling, and fresh melodies. With heartfelt lyrics and mesmerizing vocals, this song beautifully captures the essence of love, loyalty, and true emotions rooted in Haryana‚Äôs culture.

From deep emotions to unforgettable vibes, His Grace brings you a perfect balance of melody and meaning. If you love Haryanvi music with soul, this one is a must-listen!

Soulful Lyrics. Heart-touching Vibes. Pure Haryana Feels.

Song Credits:

Song Title: His Grace
Singer: Ndee Kundu & Bintu Pabra
Lyrics/Composer: Bintu Pabra
Additional Lyrics: Ndee Kundu
Music: Shine

Video By: Shubh Sandhu

#hisgrace #ndeekundu #bintupabra #newharyanvisong2025 #haryanvisong #haryanvimusic #haryanvilyrics #haryanvisinger #haryanvisong2025 #reelmusic #reelmusicharyana #haryanvitrending #trendingharyanvisong #haryanvilove #haryanvisoul

Lyrics:
Mne Jitna Kamaya Hai Sab Uski Ae Maya Hai 
Manne Jo Bhi Kmaya Hai Uski Chattar Chaya Hai

Gaam K Main Chadra Bhaar Boot Cut Dekh 
Gaadi Hai Caror‚Äôan Aali Gaadi K Main Lath Dekh 
Hater Or Choriya Ne Bha Kit Khaan Deu 
Khaati Koniya Meri Bursat Silwat Dekh 
Dil K Naram Par Boli K Hain Tedhe Bore Balcony Main R Bhang Aale Peede
Maang Le Je Pyaar T To Jaan Bhi Ye Dede Beriyan Ki Chaatiyan Pe Maar Dyan Balede

Aajya Teri Taar Dyaa Takila Nakhro Chulhe Pe Hai Chaa Ka Patila Nakhro 
Bhittar Marod Konya Ek Pise Ki Vese To Carore Ka Hai Killa Nakhro 
Nyi Nyi Chiz Jo Sikhve Jma Daily Dahn Konya Deti Mere Dil Ki Hweli 
Positivity Ki Jine Kah Dyu Hu Dukan Main Suru Te Ae Meri Sun Eke Hai Saheli 

Yaariyan Main Noota Aala Hota Kde Jikra Ni Yaar Ki Hai Mehrbaani Yaara Pe Jo Likh Rya 
Haad Mne Tode Bhi Ghane Re Tudwaye Bhi Ghne 
Par Kise Main Bhi Jaan Mere Yaara Jisa Jigra Ni 

Hisse Jo Bhi Aaya Hai Sab Uski Ae Maaya Hai 
Mne Jo Bhi Kamaya Hai Uki Chattarchya Hai 
Banda Bagwaan Ka Hu Kise Te Na Dru Main 
Thaare Aale Totkya Te Kde Koni Mru Main 
Khud Hi Kamana Mne Khud Hi Udaana 
Mkha Fer Kayate Parwa Re Duniya Ki Kru Main 

Baat Je Study Ki To Kri Mne Baarmi Baarmi K Baad Re Join Kra Army 
Mbd Ki Guide‚Äôan Te Sike Hoye Aan Royal Blood Makha Age Chale Tharvi 

Kuti Hoyi Mirch Hai R Micha Main Ghee Laasi Ki R Bhari Dhri Dekh Ketli 
Baajre Ki Roti Or Sarso Ka Saag Hai R Khaan K Main Yahe Hobby Tere Yaar Ki 

Udu Aasmaan Main Bhulya Konya Jad Meri 
Kadiya Bhi Fet Liyo Lage Konya Kad Meri 
Vo Khele Khaadya Me R Main Khelu Kalma Te 
Shillu Ki Jyu Sabda Pe Tej Hai Pakad Meri 
Maa Aale Haatha Jise Kite Bhi Swaad Ni 
Ghum Liye Duniya Re Ghar Jisi Baat Ni 
Mile Na Support Kite Bde Bhai Barga
Chache Jisa Yaar Nhi Babu Jisa Sath Nhi 

Gumaan Kre Kyaanka Main Ladla Hu Maa Ka 
Zameen‚Äôan Aale Yaar Jamidaar Nakhro Mhara To Pasina Mahange Bhaa Ka 
Ram Ki Jo Rja Hai Us Main Ae Raaji Haa
Bhoot Haare Baajiya R Bhoot Jite Baajiya 
Yaa Ae Sikhi Klla Mne Karya Bhoot Bhla Mne Loga Ki Jyu Kri Konya Kde Sosebaajiya

Hard Work Karya Hai R Dekhi Din Raat Nhi 
Dhoop Main Bhi Tape Haan R Ruke Barsaat Main Nhi 
Kaamyabi Gel Liye Ghin Ghin Badle 
Ora Ki Jyu Maari Kde Fokki Baat Baat Nhi 
Sath Mere Jitne Bhi Saare Chula Nyod Aale 
Ghar Te Bhi Bhaar Lage Gelya Khde Ghar Aale 
Kaam Bhaichaare Ke Karya Ye Ek Phone Main 
Khud Ne Dikha K Busy Kise Ke Na Kaam Tale 
Pad Jyagi Jhadjaygi Jitni Bhi Kaaya Hai 
Sath K Lejana Hai R Sath Main K Laaya Hai 
Ram Ka Vo Ghar Jime Aasn Bichya Hai 
Jitni Bhi Sampatti Hai Use Ka Kiraaya Hai 
Mne Jo Bhi Kamaya Hai Sab Uski Ae Maaya Hai 
Re Jitni Bhi Maaya Hai Uki Chattarchaaya Hai

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films‚Äô Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story‚Ä¶and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question‚Ä¶do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

snippet.title: Sukoon | Arijit Singh | Salim Sulaiman | Shraddha Pandit | Bhoomi 2025 | Merchant Records
snippet.description:
We all look around for it, but it's within us - Sukoon ü§ç "Vo Sukoon, Mujh Mein Hai"

A very special song, a feeling very close to the heart. Sung beautifully by Arijit Singh (@Official_ArijitSingh) written by Shraddha Pandit, music by Salim Sulaiman. A film by Sahil Shah.

Milton presents Bhoomi 2025, in association with Suhana Masala, supported by Megha Shrey, powered by AB Chapri Retreats

Lyrics:
Dil wohi sukoon dhoonde
Waisa hi qaraar maange 
Dil wohi sukoon dhoonde
Waisa hi qaraar maange 

Jo qudrat ne bikhere the
Bas meri raahon mein
Aur qismat ne sajaaye the
Meri nigaahon mein

Jaane ab kahaan milega 
Kahaan chhupa hoga 
Mil jaata toh rakh leta main
Apni panaahon mein

Woh sukoon shayad mujhse hi hai
Mujh mein hi tha aur mujh mein hi hai

Jhaank loon khud mein zara, sab kuch hai andar mere
Lehron pe milta nahin, jo gehre samandar mile 
Mehsoos hoga mujhe, jab khudko pehchanunga
Dil ke andar dekh kar, apni rooh ko jaanunga

Doobega‚Ä¶ Doobega‚Ä¶

Doobega toh tar jaaega
Har zarra mera
Varna tadap ke hi guzrega
Roz marra mera

Kya maine kabhi kiya hai
Thoda ishq bhi khudse 
Mil jaayega phir jo dhoondta hun 
Main darbadar kabse

Woh sukoon shayad mujhse hi hai
Mujh mein hi tha aur mujh mein hi hai
Woh sukoon shayad mujhse hi hai
Mujh mein hi tha aur mujh mein hi hai

Woh sukoon mujhse hai‚Ä¶
Mujh mein hai sukoon‚Ä¶

#Sukoon #ArijitSingh #SalimSulaiman #Bhoomi25
